sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as 调用方
    participant QWM as queryWithModel
    participant VCR as "withVCR（测试录放）"
    participant QMS as queryModelWithoutStreaming
    participant QM as "queryModel（生成器）"
    participant WR as "withRetry（生成器）"
    participant API as Anthropic API

    Caller->>QWM: systemPrompt + userPrompt
    QWM->>VCR: messages[]
    Note over VCR: 测试模式下读写 VCR 快照
    VCR->>QMS: messages + options
    QMS->>QM: 非流式路径
    QM->>WR: API 调用闭包
    loop 最多 maxRetries+1 次
        WR->>API: messages.create（非流式）
        alt 成功
            API-->>WR: AssistantMessage
            WR-->>QM: return result
        else 429/529/认证失败
            WR-->>QM: yield SystemAPIErrorMessage
        end
    end
    QM-->>QMS: AssistantMessage
    QMS-->>VCR: AssistantMessage
    VCR-->>QWM: AssistantMessage[]
    QWM-->>Caller: AssistantMessage
